* 美方因未能对平民伤亡采取可行预防措施，导致许多伊拉克平民死于轰炸和导弹袭击。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Off Target: The Conduct of the War and Civilian Casualties in Iraq|url=https://www.hrw.org/reports/2003/usa1203/4.htm|access-date=21 October 2015|work=Human Rights Watch|archive-date=2022-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220329174839/https://www.hrw.org/reports/2003/usa1203/4.htm}}</ref>
* [[美軍虐待伊拉克戰俘事件|美軍虐待伊拉克戰俘事件]]：美国陆军对关押在[[巴格达中央监狱|阿布格莱布]]的数千名伊拉克男女进行了酷刑和虐待，<ref>{{Cite news|first=Seymour M.|author=Hersh|title=Chain of Command|date=17 May 2004|url=https://www.newyorker.com/archive/2004/05/17/040517fa_fact2?currentPage=all|work=The New Yorker|accessdate=13 September 2011|quote=NBC News later quoted U.S. military officials as saying that the unreleased photographs showed American soldiers "severely beating an Iraqi prisoner nearly to death, having sex with a female Iraqi prisoner, and 'acting inappropriately with a dead body.' The officials said there also was a videotape, apparently shot by U.S. personnel, showing Iraqi guards raping young boys."|archive-date=2012-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120101055751/http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2004/05/17/040517fa_fact2?currentPage=all}}</ref>包括强奸、鸡奸、性虐待、水刑、向囚犯泼撒磷酸、剥夺睡眠和殴打。
* [[哈迪塞屠杀事件|哈迪塞屠杀事件]]：美国士兵在[[哈迪塞|哈迪塞]]杀害了了24名平民
* 联军在[[费卢杰|费卢杰]]等战役期间使用了[[白磷弹|燃烧白磷弹]]。纪录片《费卢杰，隐秘的大屠杀》声称许多伊拉克平民，包括妇女和儿童，都死于白磷烧伤。对平民使用燃烧白磷弹是明确违反国际法的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=White phosphorus melts children's flesh but no government wants to investigate—and the U.S. keeps using it, too|url=https://www.newsweek.com/why-united-nations-not-investigating-alleged-white-phosphorus-attacks-1468042|access-date=23 April 2020|author=EST|date=4 November 2019|first=Tareq Haddad On 11/4/19 at 7:17 AM|work=Newsweek|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220521151401/https://www.newsweek.com/why-united-nations-not-investigating-alleged-white-phosphorus-attacks-1468042}}</ref>美国国防部发言人巴里·维纳布尔中校否认对平民使用白磷弹，但向BBC证实了对敌方军队使用了燃烧白磷弹。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-forces-used-chemical-weapon-in-iraq-515551.html|title=US forces used 'chemical weapon' in Iraq|date=16 November 2005|work=The Independent|language=en|accessdate=26 December 2020|archive-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301191202/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-forces-used-chemical-weapon-in-iraq-515551.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Wilson|first=Jamie|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2005/nov/16/iraq.usa|title=US admits using white phosphorus in Falluja|date=16 November 2005|work=The Guardian|accessdate=23 April 2020|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2022-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220527230517/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2005/nov/16/iraq.usa}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=White phosphorus use by US-led coalition forces in Iraq condemned by humanitarian groups|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/white-phosphorus-us-led-coalition-forces-iraq-injuries-burn-muscle-bone-mosul-humanitarian-groups-a7789431.html|access-date=23 April 2020|date=14 June 2017|work=The Independent|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220420174341/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/white-phosphorus-us-led-coalition-forces-iraq-injuries-burn-muscle-bone-mosul-humanitarian-groups-a7789431.html}}</ref>
* 联军方发射了至少300,000发[[貧鈾|放射性贫铀弹]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=US fired depleted uranium at civilian areas in 2003 Iraq war, report finds|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/19/us-depleted-uranium-weapons-civilian-areas-iraq|access-date=23 April 2020|date=19 June 2014|work=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220521044552/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/19/us-depleted-uranium-weapons-civilian-areas-iraq}}</ref>2012年的几项研究表明，联军使用过贫铀弹的地区的人和其他地区的人相比有更多的畸形、癌症和其他严重健康问题。一些伊拉克医生将这些畸形归因于贫化铀的长期影响。但关于贫铀弹药是否对健康有有害健康影响在学术界依旧存在分歧。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Caputi|first=Ross|date=25 October 2012|title=The victims of Fallujah's health crisis are stifled by western silence|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2012/oct/25/fallujah-iraq-health-crisis-silence|accessdate=26 December 2020|archive-date=2022-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220418014719/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2012/oct/25/fallujah-iraq-health-crisis-silence}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Environmental pollution by depleted uranium in Iraq with special reference to Mosul and possible effects on cancer and birth defect rates|last=Fathi|first=R. A.|last2=Matti|first2=L. Y.|journal=[[Medicine,_Conflict_and_Survival|Medicine, Conflict and Survival]]|doi=10.1080/13623699.2013.765173|year=2013|volume=29|pages=7–25|pmid=23729095|last3=Al-Salih|first3=H. S.|last4=Godbold|first4=D.|number=1}}</ref>
* [[伊拉克馬赫穆迪亞美軍姦殺事件|伊拉克馬赫穆迪亞美軍姦殺事件]]：五位美国士兵强奸并杀害了14岁的伊拉克少女阿贝尔-贾纳比。之后又继续杀害了她的母亲、父亲和妹妹。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Amnesty International Report 2007, the state of the world's human rights|url=https://archive.org/details/amnestyinternati0000unse_l8p6|publisher=Amnesty International USA|year=2007|isbn=978-1-887204-46-0|location=New York, NY|pages=[https://archive.org/details/amnestyinternati0000unse_l8p6/page/143 143]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6156656.stm|title=Iraq rape soldier jailed for life|work=BBC News|date=16 November 2006|accessdate=10 September 2008|archive-date=2007-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070616163328/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6156656.stm}}</ref>
* 三名美国海军陆战队强迫平民持枪，然后把他们当作战斗人员杀害。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.iht.com/articles/2007/07/01/africa/01iraq.php|title=2 GIs charged with murder of Iraqis – International Herald Tribune|work=International Herald Tribune|accessdate=10 September 2008|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080918001602/http://www.iht.com/articles/2007/07/01/africa/01iraq.php|archivedate=18 September 2008}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Multi-National Force – Iraq – Additional Soldier charged with murder|url=http://www.mnf-iraq.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=12658&Itemid=128|access-date=10 September 2008|publisher=Mnf-iraq.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070816140724/http://www.mnf-iraq.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=12658&Itemid=128|archive-date=16 August 2007}}</ref>据''[[国家_(杂志)|《国家报》]]''报道，美军士兵还目睹了许多其他类似行为。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thenation.com/article/archive/other-war-iraq-vets-bear-witness-0/|title=The Other War: Iraq Vets Bear Witness|work=The Nation|author=Chris Hedges|accessdate=10 September 2008|authorlink=Chris Hedges|archive-date=2022-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220514085820/https://www.thenation.com/article/archive/other-war-iraq-vets-bear-witness-0/}}</ref>
* [[黑水公司巴格達槍擊案|黑水公司巴格達槍擊案]]：美军聘请的私人军事公司'''黑水国际'''在巴格达杀害了17名伊拉克平民。
* 公共利益律师和欧洲宪法与人权中心于2014年1月12日向[[国际刑事法院|国际刑事法院]]提交了关于英国军队殴打、电击、模拟处决和[[性侵犯|性侵犯]]囚犯的指控。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/exclusive-devastating-dossier-on-abuse-by-uk-forces-in-iraq-goes-to-international-criminal-court-9053735.html|title=Exclusive: Devastating dossier on 'abuse' by UK forces in Iraq goes to International Criminal Court|work=The Independent|date=12 January 2014|location=London|first=Jonathan|author=Owen|accessdate=2022-03-05|archive-date=2022-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220331181048/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/exclusive-devastating-dossier-on-abuse-by-uk-forces-in-iraq-goes-to-international-criminal-court-9053735.html}}</ref>

=== 反美武装 ===
据伊政府部长Bayan Jabr的公布，2005年1月－2006年6月，共有12000名伊拉克人死于自杀炸弹和反美武装的其他攻击<ref>Ellen Knickmeyer (2005-06-03). "Iraq Puts Civilian Toll at 12,000". The Washington Post. http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/06/02/AR2005060201098.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/06/02/AR2005060201098.html|date=20210204221419}}.</ref>。

2003年8月在巴格达有一名联合国专员和21名联合国人员被杀害<ref>Who are the Iraq Insurgents?". NewsHour with Jim Lehrer. 2006-06-12.</ref>。有两名阿尔及利亚外交人员Ali Belaroussi和Azzedine Belkadi被斩首<ref>Kidnappers Kill Algerian Diplomats". Free Internet Press. 2005-07-27. {{cite web|title=存档副本|url=https://freeinternetpress.com/story.php?sid=4107|accessdate=2008-10-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927235252/https://freeinternetpress.com/story.php?sid=4107|archivedate=2007-09-27|deadurl=yes}}.</ref>。

2006年2月炸弹袭击al-Askari清真寺，死亡165人，激发了报复狂潮<ref>Alex Rodriguez, Iraqi shrine blast suspect caught (paid archive), The Chicago Tribune June 29, 2006.</ref>。

有如下非军事人员被杀害：翻译[[金鲜一|金鲜一]]（韩，被斩首），游客[[香田证生|香田证生]]（日，被斩首），Fabrizio Quattrocchi（意），义工Margaret Hassan，Nick Berg，摄影师Salvatore Santoro（意）和伊拉克人Seif Adnan Kanaan<ref>Foreign hostages in Iraq". CBC News. 2006-06-22. http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/iraq/hostages.html#killed {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/iraq/hostages.html#killed|date=20060807115040}}.</ref>。四名佣兵Scott Helvenston、Jerko Zovko、Wesley Batalona和Michael Teague被杀后，用车拖着点燃的尸体开过大街，并被吊起来示众<ref>"4 Contractors murdered by al Qaeda". Washingtonpost.com. 2004-03-31. http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/mmedia/apdaily/033104-11v.htm {{Wayback|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/mmedia/apdaily/033104-11v.htm|date=20201215025703}}. Retrieved 2010-10-23.</ref>。

== 影响 ==
=== 国际反应 ===
[[File:State_positions_Iraq_war.svg|thumb]]}}{{legend|#ea6400|[[伊拉克多国部队|进军伊拉克的多国联军]]}}{{legend|#fad91f|支持联军进军伊拉克的国家}}{{legend|#0f83bb|谴责联军进军伊拉克的国家}}{{legend|#ababab|中立或未知立场}}]]
有49个国家支持该军事行动。参加地面战的国家有[[美国|美国]]、[[英国|英国]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]和[[波兰|波兰]]，[[丹麦|丹麦]]政府亦对[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]宣战，并派遣了两艘军舰支援美军。[[韩国|韩国]]、[[日本|日本]]、[[意大利|意大利]]、[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]等多个国家提供后勤支援。

这场战争遭到[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[法國|法國]]、[[德國|德國]]、[[阿拉伯国家联盟|阿拉伯国家联盟]]、[[不结盟运动|不结盟运动]]等多国政府和国际组织的批评与谴责。

[[奥地利|奥地利]]等多个歐洲国家宣称，对伊拉克的军事行动由于没有得到联合国安理会的授权，已经违反了国际法。[[埃及|埃及]]籍的联合国前秘书长[[布特罗斯·加利|布特罗斯·加利]]谴责该军事行动，认为违反了[[联合国宪章|联合国宪章]]。奥地利、[[瑞士|瑞士]]、[[伊朗|伊朗]]、[[比利時|比利時]]等國禁止联军战机飞越其领空，[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]禁止美军导弹通过其领空袭击伊拉克。[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]在国际及联合国会议上严重谴责[[美国|美国]]及[[英国|英国]]的军事报复行动。

=== 反战 ===
[[File:The_logic_of_Iraq_war_by_Latuff2.jpg|450px]]
全球普遍的反战情绪最终导致了[[全球反对对伊战争大游行|全球反对对伊战争大游行]]。

2015年，英國前首相[[東尼·布萊爾|東尼·布萊爾]]和前美國駐伊拉克指揮官[[麥可·T·佛林|麥可·T·佛林]]表示發動伊拉克戰爭是錯誤的，且導致了之後出現[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20151025/718512/ |title=布萊爾道歉：伊拉克戰爭是個錯誤 |accessdate=2017-10-23 |archive-date=2017-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023120158/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20151025/718512/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20151205/746871/ |title=美國12年前的錯誤讓IS坐大 |accessdate=2017-10-23 |archive-date=2017-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023115654/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20151205/746871/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 调查 ==
2007年2月9日，[[美国国防部|美国国防部]]向国会提交一份关于伊拉克战争前情报的内部调查报告。报告认定，有关萨达姆与[[基地组织|基地组织]]存在明显联系的评估，無論是品質或可信度都是可疑的。這是因為美國国防部副部长道格拉斯·费思所采取的不恰当行为，才得到这個错误结论，但调查报告认为他没有触犯法律。<ref>徐超，[http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2007-02/11/content_5725044.htm 五角大楼:伊战前情报不实 "不当"但"不违法"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2007-02/11/content_5725044.htm |date=20080726095159 }}，新华网</ref>根据维基解密在2010年10月22日所公布的美军文件显示，在伊拉克战争期间直接死于战火的平民达6万6081人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://udn.com/NEWS/WORLD/WOR3/5929674.shtml|language=|title=维基解密再爆料，伊战6.6万平民惨死|publisher=联合报|date=2010-10-24|accessdate=|archive-date=2011-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110101221736/http://udn.com/NEWS/WORLD/WOR3/5929674.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年7月6日，調查2003年伊拉克戰爭中英國責任的報告《[[齊爾考特報告|齊爾考特報告]]》正式出爐，該報告歷時7年完工。當天，主導報告制定的調查委員會主席{{le|約翰·齊爾考特|John Chilcot}}勳爵親自宣布報告的相關調查結果。報告認為，基於情報錯誤，2003年伊拉克並沒有擁有對世界構成威脅的大規模殺傷性武器（[[WMD|WMD]]），伊拉克領導人薩達姆當時也沒有對西方世界構成所謂的「迫在眉睫的威脅」。2003年3月，美英正是因為伊拉克擁有[[WMD|WMD]]為藉口，繞過聯合國，對伊拉克發動空襲，由此開啟了長達8年的伊拉克戰爭。

